{
  "stem": "26983.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The use lead, after Fredy Hirsch, was also somebody still from Thereseinstadt separate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, we were very sad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Fredy Hirsch was a demigod for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had saved us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because his way of education, to keep us trim, to make exercises, is-- and if we were a bit dirty, he looked in our nails.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he forced us to wash ourselves, even with snow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember we had not a towel, a group of 20 children had a handkerchief.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was hardly any water running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But his drilling, in a-- in a way, oppression drilling, saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because in Auschwitz, of course, the people who somehow survived had a better chance to survive if they looked more or less still human, or according to the German or Nazi conception of cleanliness, human, and tidiness.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And if you looked somehow starting to be what we called a muselmann, or you had a little rash, that would mean you go to the gas chambers in the next-- or also you would be hit, or you got much worse treatment than somebody who still looked half human.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the many reasons why we survived is because he drilled us to keep fit, even in these circumstances.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because who wanted in Auschwitz to wash himself with snow, or look [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he very much stressed this point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now afterwards was another [INAUDIBLE] that was the head of the block, [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sepel. ?] And [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we somehow continued our life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Miriam Edelstein, it was the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wife of Jacob Edelstein, was also the mother of the block after Hanka who went to gas.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
